ISLAMABAD, Mar 05 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain Saturday said the Pakistan Tehreek-i-Insaf (PTI) had launched a vibrant and much-awaited movement under the banner of ‘Huqooq-e-Sindh March’ to ensure the public rights, which were being denied by the provincial government since long.
In a tweet, the minister asked the PTI workers to stand up and get the Sindh rights by downing the idols of oppression and barbarism.
